## Module 5 — Tenants

| ID | Test Case | Steps | Expected Result | Result |
|----|-----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| TNT-01 | List all tenants | 1. Go to `/tenants` | All tenants listed with contract count. Paginated at 20. | |
| TNT-02 | Search tenants | 1. Go to `/tenants`<br>2. Type a name, phone, or national ID into the search box<br>3. Submit | Only matching tenants shown. | |
| TNT-03 | Create tenant – valid | 1. Go to `/tenants/create`<br>2. Fill all required fields (name, national ID, phone)<br>3. Submit | Redirected to tenant detail. Success message shown. | |
| TNT-04 | Create tenant – with photo | 1. Go to `/tenants/create`<br>2. Fill fields and upload a photo<br>3. Submit | Photo stored. Shown on tenant detail page. | |
| TNT-05 | Create tenant – name required | 1. Submit the create form without a name | Validation error for name field. | |
| TNT-06 | View tenant detail | 1. Click a tenant | Detail page shows personal info, all contracts, and rent schedule summaries. | |
| TNT-07 | Edit tenant | 1. Open a tenant → **Edit**<br>2. Update phone number<br>3. Submit | Updated info shown. Success message. | |
| TNT-08 | Edit tenant – replace photo | 1. Open a tenant with a photo → **Edit**<br>2. Upload a new photo<br>3. Submit | Old photo replaced. New photo displayed. | |
| TNT-09 | Delete tenant | 1. Open a tenant<br>2. Click **Delete** | Tenant soft-deleted. No longer in list. | |

