## Module 8 — Payments

| ID | Test Case | Steps | Expected Result | Result |
|----|-----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| PAY-01 | List payments | 1. Go to `/payments` | All payment records listed with tenant, schedule, amount, and date. | |
| PAY-02 | Filter payments by contract | 1. Go to `/payments`<br>2. Select a contract from filter | Only payments for that contract shown. | |
| PAY-03 | Record full payment | 1. Open a pending rent schedule<br>2. Click **Record Payment**<br>3. Enter the full due amount<br>4. Set payment date<br>5. Submit | Payment recorded. Schedule status → **Paid**. Redirected to receipt page. | |
| PAY-04 | Record partial payment | 1. Same as PAY-03 but enter an amount less than the due amount | Payment recorded. Schedule status → **Partial**. Receipt shown. | |
| PAY-05 | Payment amount must be positive | 1. Go to payment form<br>2. Enter 0 or negative amount<br>3. Submit | Validation error: amount must be positive. | |
| PAY-06 | View receipt | 1. After recording payment, view receipt page | Receipt shows: tenant name, unit, building, amount paid, date, collected by. | |
| PAY-07 | Download receipt PDF | 1. On the receipt page, click **Download PDF** | PDF file (`receipt-{id}.pdf`) downloaded. Contains correct payment details. | |

