## Module 10 — Reports

| ID | Test Case | Steps | Expected Result | Result |
|----|-----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| RPT-01 | Open reports page | 1. Go to `/reports` | Page loads showing summary cards: this month's income, overdue total, active contracts, occupancy rate. | |
| RPT-02 | Payments report – no filter | 1. Go to `/reports`<br>2. Select type = **Payments**<br>3. Submit without date range | All payments listed on the page. | |
| RPT-03 | Payments report – date range | 1. Select type = **Payments**<br>2. Enter from/to date<br>3. Submit | Only payments within that date range shown. | |
| RPT-04 | Payments report – building filter | 1. Select type = **Payments** + choose a building<br>2. Submit | Only payments for units in that building shown. | |
| RPT-05 | Contracts report | 1. Select type = **Contracts**<br>2. Submit | All contracts listed with tenant and unit. | |
| RPT-06 | Contracts report – status filter | 1. Select type = **Contracts** + status = **Active** | Only active contracts shown. | |
| RPT-07 | Export payments to Excel | 1. On the payments report page, click **Export Excel** | `.xlsx` file downloaded. Contains correct payment records. | |
| RPT-08 | Export contracts to Excel | 1. On the contracts report page, click **Export Excel** | `.xlsx` file downloaded. Contains correct contract records. | |
| RPT-09 | Occupancy rate is correct | 1. Note number of rented vs total units<br>2. Open `/reports` | Occupancy rate = (rented ÷ total) × 100, rounded to 1 decimal. | |

