## Module 11 — User Management

| ID | Test Case | Steps | Expected Result | Result |
|----|-----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| USER-01 | List users | 1. Go to `/users` | All users shown with their roles. Paginated at 15. | |
| USER-02 | Create user – valid | 1. Go to `/users/create`<br>2. Fill name, email, password, confirm password, select role<br>3. Submit | User created. Redirected to `/users`. Success message. | |
| USER-03 | Create user – email must be unique | 1. Try creating a user with an email already in the system | Validation error: "The email has already been taken." | |
| USER-04 | Create user – password min 8 chars | 1. Enter a password with fewer than 8 characters | Validation error on password field. | |
| USER-05 | Create user – password confirmation | 1. Enter mismatched password and confirmation | Validation error. | |
| USER-06 | Edit user | 1. Click **Edit** on a user<br>2. Change their phone<br>3. Submit | User updated. Success message. | |
| USER-07 | Change user role | 1. Edit a user<br>2. Change their role<br>3. Submit | User's role updated. Reflected on user list. | |
| USER-08 | Deactivate user | 1. Edit a user<br>2. Uncheck **Active**<br>3. Submit | `is_active` = false. User can no longer log in. | |
| USER-09 | Change user password | 1. Edit a user<br>2. Enter new password + confirmation<br>3. Submit | Password changed. User can log in with the new password. | |

