## Cross-Cutting & Security

| ID | Test Case | Steps | Expected Result | Result |
|----|-----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| SEC-01 | Unauthenticated access to all protected routes | 1. Log out<br>2. Try to visit `/dashboard`, `/buildings`, `/units`, `/tenants`, `/contracts`, `/payments`, `/maintenance`, `/reports`, `/users`, `/audit-log` | All routes redirect to `/login`. | |
| SEC-02 | Pagination on large datasets | 1. Create 20+ buildings<br>2. Visit `/buildings` | First 15 shown with working "Next" pagination link. | |
| SEC-03 | Flash success messages | 1. Perform any create/update/delete action | Green success flash message visible at top of page after redirect. | |
| SEC-04 | Flash error messages | 1. Submit an invalid form | Red error messages shown per field. | |
| SEC-05 | Arabic content rendering | 1. Create records with Arabic names (e.g., `برج النخيل`) | Arabic text saved and displayed correctly with RTL layout. | |
